  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "Riley's Rangers, Magistracy-affiliated mercenaries, built this one themselves out of Firefly Foundry before they had proper facilities, which tells you something about how much the Blackjack meant to them. The BJ-1 bones are all still there but everything worth keeping got upgraded. LB-Xs instead of the old AC/2s, ER lasers, double heat sinks. It's a labor of love as much as a fighting machine. Rangers flew this thing with pride and honestly, looking at it, I get why.",
